=== UUID Casting Fixes ===
Fixed pre-existing bug where string-typed IDs from api-types crate were bound to UUID columns
without explicit casts. PostgreSQL requires explicit TEXT->UUID casting in INSERT/UPDATE contexts.
Added `::uuid` casts throughout:
- crates/server/src/engine/jobs.rs (all WHERE id = $1 queries)
- crates/server/src/engine/mod.rs (all INSERT/SELECT queries with UUID columns)
- crates/server/src/routes/sessions.rs (all WHERE id = $1 on sessions/jobs tables, INSERT with UUID cols)
- crates/server/src/routes/tasks.rs (all new queries)
